Package com.example.finding_tory

Class Inventory

java.lang.Object
com.example.finding_tory.Inventory
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Inventory extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an inventory containing a collection of items. This class provides functionalities to manage an inventory, such as adding, removing, and accessing items. It also calculates the total estimated value of all items in the inventory.
